STATE
v.
Lorenzo DUARTE. No. 653P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 26, 2006. Daniel P. O'Brien, Assistant Attorney General, Jeff Hunt, District Attorney, for State. William D. Auman, for Duarte.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 16th day of December 2005 by Defendant for Appeal:

"Motion Dismissed ex mero motu by order of the Court in conference this the 26th day of January 2006."
